Insider Activity


Individual




David Thomas Seaton



Mr. David T. Seaton is Independent Director at The Mosaic Co., Chairman & Chief Executive Officer at Fluor Corp., Chairman-Southwest Region at Boys & Girls Clubs of America, Chief Executive Officer & Director at Fluor Enterprises, Inc., Director-Partnering Against Corruption Initiative at World Economic Forum, a Member at The Business Roundtable, a Member at The International Business Council and President at Fluor Federal Services, Inc. He is on the Board of Directors at The Mosaic Co., Fluor Enterprises, Inc., American Petroleum Institute, Inc., Fluor Foundation and U.S.-Saudi Arabian Business Council. Mr. Seaton was previously employed as Managing Director & Vice President by Fluor Arabia Ltd. He also served on the board at Mosaic Co. /Old/ and GNS II (US) Corp. He received his undergraduate degree from the University of South Carolina.



